.TH "nvme_init_virtual_mgmt" 9 "nvme_init_virtual_mgmt" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_virtual_mgmt \- Initialize passthru command for Virtualization Resource Management
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_virtual_mgmt
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "enum nvme_virt_mgmt_act act "  ","
.BI "enum nvme_virt_mgmt_rt rt "  ","
.BI "__u16 cntlid "  ","
.BI "__u16 nr "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "act" 12
Virtual resource action, see \fIenum nvme_virt_mgmt_act\fP
.IP "rt" 12
Resource type to modify, see \fIenum nvme_virt_mgmt_rt\fP
.IP "cntlid" 12
Controller id for which resources are bing modified
.IP "nr" 12
Number of resources being allocated or assigned
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Virtualization
Management command.
